snippet.title: Skytorn Teaser
snippet.description:
Skytorn is a procedurally generated action adventure game, set in the ruins of a fallen world.
Coming to PS4 and PC (and eventually Mac / Linux)
http://skytorngame.com/

Trailer music by Alec Holowka http://infiniteammo.ca/
